('98162','33871','5','Modern villa with spectacular sea views in Santa Ponsa'),
('98163','33872','5','This modern villa is located in Santa Ponsa, in a southerly direction and was created in 2015. The German developers attached great importance to the processing of high quality materials and expert execution. The villa stands on a rocky hillside and has 2 residential floors (approx 350sqm), 1 spa or guest apartment approx 50m² and a parking garage with space for 3 cars. From the garage all levels can be reached by elevator. The living level offers living-dining room and a kitchen (with breakfast terrace) also a small indoor pool with a shower and a partially covered terrace. The villa comes with 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms as well as the expansion opportunity for a guest room with bathroom and kitchenette on a separate level. Features include underfloor heating (water), solar assisted heat pump, air conditioning h / c, double glazed aluminum sliding panoramic doors, elevator and roof terrace with barbecue'),
